WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:12.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:40.600 --> 00:43.410
- (THUMPING)
- (GROWLING, MUFFLED)

00:50.560 --> 00:53.769
(THUMPING CONTINUES)

01:04.680 --> 01:06.284
MAN: Father Barrow?

01:08.600 --> 01:12.060
Father James asks if you're ready.
He needs you now.

01:12.160 --> 01:14.367
(MAN 2 SPEAKING, INDISTINCT)

01:21.840 --> 01:23.888
(MAN 2 CONTINUES)

01:25.880 --> 01:27.848
(GROWLING CONTINUES)

01:35.480 --> 01:36.970
Will you be joining us?

01:37.920 --> 01:39.445
I fear not.

01:42.440 --> 01:45.046
(ROARING)

01:46.640 --> 01:49.723
(GROWLING, SNARLING)

02:00.280 --> 02:03.900
MAN 2: Depart, accursed one.
Depart with all your deceits.

02:04.000 --> 02:05.860
Depart then, transgressor.

02:05.960 --> 02:09.900
Depart, seducer,
full of lies and cunning,

02:10.000 --> 02:13.580
foe of virtue,
persecutor of the innocent.

02:13.680 --> 02:15.940
Give place, abominable creature.

02:16.040 --> 02:18.820
Give way, you monster.
Give way to Christ,

02:18.920 --> 02:20.460
in whom you found none of your works.

02:20.560 --> 02:22.740
- (WATER SIZZLING)
- (GROWLING)

02:23.840 --> 02:27.700
For he has already stripped you of your
powers and laid waste your kingdom,

02:27.800 --> 02:31.088
bound you prisoner
and plundered your weapons.

02:33.120 --> 02:35.964
He has cast you forth
into the outer darkness,

02:37.560 --> 02:40.564
where everlasting ruin
awaits you and your abettors.

02:42.280 --> 02:45.020
- To what purpose do you insolently resist?
- (GROANS)

02:45.120 --> 02:48.408
To what purpose do you brazenly refuse?

02:48.520 --> 02:51.180
For you are guilty before Almighty God,

02:51.280 --> 02:53.100
whose laws you have transgressed.

02:53.200 --> 02:56.820
You are guilty before his Son,
our Lord Jesus Christ,

02:56.920 --> 02:58.500
whom you presumed to tempt.

02:58.600 --> 03:01.220
You are guilty
before the whole human race,

03:01.320 --> 03:05.380
to whom you proffered by your
enticements the poison cup of death.

03:05.480 --> 03:07.084
BOTH: Amen.

03:09.320 --> 03:11.288
Is the cochon prepared?

03:12.800 --> 03:14.484
Expulsion is near.

03:15.600 --> 03:18.180
Therefore, I adjure you,
profligate dragon,

03:18.280 --> 03:21.020
in the name of the spotless Lamb,

03:21.120 --> 03:23.180
who has trodden down the asp
and the basilisk...

03:23.280 --> 03:25.420
and overcome the lion and the dragon,

03:25.520 --> 03:29.445
to depart from this woman
and her unborn child,

03:32.040 --> 03:34.884
to depart from the church of God.

03:38.320 --> 03:41.060
And when he had cast you out,
you did not even dare,

03:41.160 --> 03:42.820
except by his leave,

03:42.920 --> 03:44.620
to enter into a herd of swine.

03:44.720 --> 03:47.100
And now, as I adjure you in his name,

03:47.200 --> 03:50.060
begone from this woman and her
unborn child... (CONTINUES, INDISTINCT)

03:50.160 --> 03:52.220
(GUTTURAL VOICE) Please help me.

03:52.320 --> 03:54.100
(NORMAL VOICE) Help me. Save me.

03:54.200 --> 03:57.044
My baby. Let me go.

03:59.000 --> 04:01.380
Depart then, impious one...

04:01.480 --> 04:06.260
My baby. Let me go. Please.
Do what you know is right.

04:06.360 --> 04:07.980
For my baby.

04:08.080 --> 04:11.527
Everything's gonna be okay. Trust me.

04:13.440 --> 04:18.367
- (GROWLING)
- Father, please. The baby is coming.

04:19.200 --> 04:22.300
Help me. Please.

04:22.400 --> 04:25.006
Do what's right! (WHIMPERING)

04:26.520 --> 04:28.522
Yes. Yes.

04:31.160 --> 04:32.660
(SNARLS)

04:32.760 --> 04:34.649
...give place to the Lord Jesus Christ,

04:36.400 --> 04:39.210
- who shed his most precious blood for man.
- (WHIMPERING)

04:40.640 --> 04:43.723
She's going into labor.
We have to help her. (VOICE ECHOING)

04:47.880 --> 04:49.900
...from whose sight nothing is hidden.

04:50.000 --> 04:53.900
It is he who repels you,
to whose might all things are subject.

04:54.000 --> 04:56.571
(WOMAN'S VOICE) Please, Father. Help me.

04:58.880 --> 05:01.087
Please. Do what's right.

05:07.520 --> 05:09.727
Please, Father.

05:16.800 --> 05:18.404
(GUTTURAL CACKLING)

05:21.560 --> 05:23.210
What are you doing, Father?

05:33.440 --> 05:36.125
Father, you will always be
a fool for the flesh!

05:37.160 --> 05:39.640
- (SCREECHES)
- No!

06:13.920 --> 06:15.340
What have you done?

06:15.440 --> 06:18.808
My wife. My baby.

06:23.680 --> 06:25.648
(SOBBING)

07:13.320 --> 07:15.322
(LOCK CLICKS)

07:16.560 --> 07:18.085
(HANDLE RATTLES)

07:26.520 --> 07:29.126
- Good evening, Father.
- Evening to you, Elliott.

07:29.240 --> 07:33.882
- (SCREAMING, FAINT)
- WOMAN ON PA: Lights out in 15 minutes.

07:41.280 --> 07:43.203
(LOCK CLICKS)

07:50.880 --> 07:52.980
I'm Henry Davies.

07:53.080 --> 07:55.180
I'm the chaplain at Clovesdale.

07:55.280 --> 07:57.220
And my attorney tells me
you're the guy to thank...

07:57.320 --> 07:59.020
for being transferred here
instead of prison.

07:59.120 --> 08:02.980
It was nothing. I play basketball
with the attorney general.

08:03.080 --> 08:07.688
I convinced him that you'd be...
best in a Catholic-run institution.

08:07.840 --> 08:12.721
Besides, it was you who had to accept
the plea of insanity to make this work.

08:13.760 --> 08:16.420
Look. (SIGHS)

08:16.520 --> 08:19.540
I received official notice
from the Vatican, and, uh,

08:19.640 --> 08:23.042
I've been instructed
to pass it over to you.

08:25.320 --> 08:28.020
You've been dismissed
from your clerical state.

08:28.120 --> 08:30.407
By papal decree, no less.

08:31.800 --> 08:33.299
"From this moment forth,

08:33.400 --> 08:36.961
you are expressly forbidden
from exercising ministerial functions."

08:37.120 --> 08:39.380
- Yeah.
- Sorry.

08:39.480 --> 08:41.820
I did all I could.

08:41.919 --> 08:44.207
So I'm no longer a priest.

08:47.960 --> 08:50.361
You understand the decree
that's been handed down to you?

08:50.480 --> 08:53.420
- Yes, I do.
- Very well.

08:53.520 --> 08:55.260
(SIGHS)

08:55.360 --> 08:58.091
May God watch over your soul,
John Barrow.

09:02.920 --> 09:05.366
John, I'm going to be retiring soon.

09:07.000 --> 09:11.801
Until I do, I'm gonna be saying mass
every day in the chapel at 8:00 AM.

09:12.680 --> 09:14.444
You're welcome to join us.

09:15.480 --> 09:16.686
Thank you.

09:23.440 --> 09:26.011
(DOOR CLOSES, LOCKS)

09:32.200 --> 09:34.567
♪♪ (SPEAKERS: ELECTRONIC DANCE)

09:43.360 --> 09:45.860
- Party hearty!
- ALL: Yay!

09:45.960 --> 09:48.088
Luckiest girl
in the whole wide world, right?

09:48.200 --> 09:50.248
- Cheers.
- ALL: Happy birthday!

09:50.360 --> 09:53.364
(ALL SHOUTING, HOOTING)

09:58.840 --> 10:00.300
Whoo! (COUGHS)

10:00.400 --> 10:02.420
Oh, my God. (LAUGHS)

10:02.520 --> 10:04.580
You guys, six years ago,
I never would have thought...

10:04.680 --> 10:06.980
that I would be here,
doing this on my birthday.

10:07.080 --> 10:08.540
Thank you so much.

10:08.640 --> 10:10.340
The youngest woman to make partner...

10:10.440 --> 10:12.940
deserves to let loose
on her 24th birthday.

10:13.040 --> 10:14.980
(ALL CHEERING, LAUGHING)

10:15.080 --> 10:17.140
Nobody anywhere has ever
made partner below 30.

10:17.240 --> 10:19.140
Do you know how fortunate
you are right now?

10:19.240 --> 10:21.740
You would not have said that
if you knew me in high school.

10:21.840 --> 10:23.410
- Right?
- Yeah.

10:25.360 --> 10:27.886
- You're the best.
- (LAUGHING)

10:31.880 --> 10:35.043
- Hey.
- Hey! Lydia!

10:36.760 --> 10:37.780
Yeah.

10:37.880 --> 10:40.580
Molly, meet Lydia. Lydia, Molly.

10:40.680 --> 10:42.011
Hi.

10:42.120 --> 10:45.660
It is Molly's birthday, and get this...
She just made partner.

10:45.760 --> 10:49.700
- Happy birthday. It's really nice to meet you.
- Thank you.

10:49.800 --> 10:51.940
- WOMAN: It's getting late. Let's go home.
- Okay. Here.

10:52.040 --> 10:53.530
Have a shot.

10:56.200 --> 10:57.690
So are you always this much fun?

10:57.800 --> 10:59.928
You have no idea. Come here.

11:04.720 --> 11:07.246
(NO AUDIBLE DIALOGUE)

12:22.000 --> 12:24.140
Oh. No, no, no, no, no.

12:24.240 --> 12:26.260
- WOMAN: Hey! Jerk!
- (KNOCKING)

12:26.360 --> 12:29.967
Let us in! Hey! Open the door!

12:53.000 --> 12:55.980
Come on. Let's dance.

12:56.080 --> 12:58.367
- (KNOCKING CONTINUES)
- All right. All right, all right, all right!

12:59.960 --> 13:01.530
(CHUCKLES)

13:09.400 --> 13:10.811
(CHUCKLES)

13:12.280 --> 13:13.805
Happy 24th.

13:15.120 --> 13:16.963
♪♪ (SPEAKERS: ELECTRONIC DANCE)

13:25.520 --> 13:27.602
'Scuse us. 'Scuse us. Molly!

13:28.560 --> 13:31.291
Molly! Molly!

13:33.080 --> 13:36.940
- Maybe you should go home.
- Oh, that's a good idea.

13:37.040 --> 13:38.451
You guys wanna come home?

13:38.560 --> 13:39.540
- Yeah.
- Oh, yeah.

13:39.640 --> 13:42.540
Molly! Molly!

13:42.640 --> 13:45.246
Let's go. Molly, we're leaving!

13:48.040 --> 13:50.247
- Molly!
- Forget it. Come on. Let's go.

13:57.440 --> 13:58.930
(LAUGHING)

14:00.760 --> 14:02.330
Oh, snap.

14:03.920 --> 14:05.380
It's not bad.

14:05.480 --> 14:07.220
MOLLY: Come here.

14:07.320 --> 14:08.685
Hey. (LAUGHS)

14:14.840 --> 14:15.921
Come here.

14:25.080 --> 14:26.140
Enough.

14:26.240 --> 14:27.969
Go to the bed.

14:35.920 --> 14:37.285
- That's lovely.
- (LAUGHING)

14:38.840 --> 14:40.740
Say, "Happy birthday."

14:40.840 --> 14:42.140
Happy birthday.

14:42.240 --> 14:43.740
Say it again.

14:43.840 --> 14:45.080
Happy birthday.

14:57.040 --> 14:58.804
Okay. Enough. Go to the bed.

15:20.200 --> 15:21.740
You gonna join us, or what?

15:21.840 --> 15:23.001
LYDIA: Yeah.

15:37.560 --> 15:39.164
(KNOCKING)

15:46.480 --> 15:49.211
(KNOCKING CONTINUES)

15:54.360 --> 15:57.011
(KNOCKING CONTINUES)

16:05.160 --> 16:07.128
- (KNOCKING CONTINUES)
- Just a second.

16:17.120 --> 16:18.406
(SIGHS)

16:22.960 --> 16:25.460
- Ms. Hartley?
- Yeah.

16:25.560 --> 16:28.620
We got a lot of complaints about noise
from your neighbors early this morning.

16:28.720 --> 16:30.180
You having a party?

16:30.980 --> 16:33.820
Oh, no. I was celebrating my birthday.
(CLEARS THROAT)

16:33.920 --> 16:36.180
You mind if we come in
and take a look around?

16:36.280 --> 16:38.408
No. No. Come on in.

16:41.640 --> 16:43.100
FEMALE OFFICER:
We've also had complaints...

16:43.200 --> 16:45.460
about shouting and yelling
coming from your apartment.

16:45.560 --> 16:47.403
MOLLY: Sorry, Officer.

16:53.520 --> 16:57.445
- (SCRATCHING)
- (VOICES, INDISTINCT)

16:59.880 --> 17:01.245
You okay?

17:02.560 --> 17:04.780
Y-Yeah. I'm fine. (CLEARS THROAT)

17:04.880 --> 17:07.486
I'm a little bit hungover, but yeah.

17:08.920 --> 17:10.859
Okay. Well, please stay here
while I look around. All right?

17:10.960 --> 17:11.961
Yes, ma'am.

17:16.560 --> 17:19.450
(SCRATCHING, VOICES CONTINUE)

17:47.000 --> 17:48.729
(GROWLING)

18:03.080 --> 18:04.206
(GAGS) Oh!

18:08.840 --> 18:09.841
Oh.

18:10.680 --> 18:12.170
I got two!

18:13.920 --> 18:18.260
We have a double 187. One male,
early 30s. One female, late 20s.

18:18.360 --> 18:20.362
Who are they? Do you know them?

18:21.400 --> 18:23.209
Yeah. Yeah.

18:24.240 --> 18:25.700
Did you kill them?

18:25.800 --> 18:27.700
(POLICE RADIO CHATTER)

18:27.800 --> 18:29.500
No.

18:29.600 --> 18:32.020
If you didn't kill them,
Ms. Hartley, then who did?

18:32.120 --> 18:34.521
(VOICES, SCRATCHING RESUME)

18:42.240 --> 18:43.940
You don't hear that?

18:44.040 --> 18:46.060
No. I don't hear anything.

18:46.160 --> 18:49.660
This is gonna go a whole lot better for you
if you just tell us what happened here.

18:49.760 --> 18:51.842
(VOICES, SCRATCHING CONTINUE)

18:52.480 --> 18:58.249
(VOICES, GROWLING)

19:18.000 --> 19:19.780
You want to know
what happened last night?

19:19.880 --> 19:21.420
Yes.

19:21.520 --> 19:23.204
I didn't kill them.

19:24.240 --> 19:25.220
We did.

19:25.320 --> 19:26.700
"We"?

19:26.800 --> 19:28.290
(DISTORTED VOICE) We.

19:29.360 --> 19:31.442
- I've heard enough. Let's go.
- Uh, Sam.

19:32.560 --> 19:34.050
You're bleeding.

19:36.960 --> 19:38.121
It's happening.

19:41.640 --> 19:43.620
MALE OFFICER: What's happening?

19:43.720 --> 19:45.180
(DISTORTED VOICE) We're here.

19:45.280 --> 19:46.850
FEMALE OFFICER: What did she say?

19:49.440 --> 19:50.601
We're here!

20:10.440 --> 20:12.488
(BIRD CAWING)

20:14.760 --> 20:17.570
(BIRDS CAWING)

20:48.520 --> 20:51.660
BARROW: Dear Heavenly Father,
thank you for this day.

20:51.760 --> 20:54.206
Thank you for my being able
to wake once again,

20:55.200 --> 20:58.980
to see and to hear this morning.

20:59.080 --> 21:00.241
- Amen.
- Amen.

21:04.200 --> 21:05.531
(SIGHS)

21:07.360 --> 21:09.283
I'm proud of you, Barrow.

21:09.400 --> 21:14.486
A man of lesser faith would have turned his
back on God after what you've been through.

21:15.600 --> 21:18.968
Excuse me while I make my final rounds.

21:19.080 --> 21:22.220
What are you gonna do with all your free
time once you've retired from this place?

21:22.320 --> 21:24.780
I'll be teaching at a local seminary,

21:24.880 --> 21:27.660
where there's a residency awaiting me.

21:27.760 --> 21:29.940
Besides that, what else?

21:30.040 --> 21:33.540
Drinking a lot of beer,
playing a lot of basketball.

21:33.640 --> 21:35.740
Which you're welcome to do with me...

21:35.840 --> 21:37.888
when they release you from this place.

21:38.680 --> 21:39.841
Thanks.

22:15.600 --> 22:18.500
(SHOUTING, FAINT) No! No! No!

22:18.600 --> 22:20.762
(LAUGHING, FAINT)

22:23.680 --> 22:26.809
(SHOUTING, FAINT)

22:28.480 --> 22:30.084
Hartley, Molly.

22:33.520 --> 22:37.127
You are being held here for a court-ordered
evaluation. It's for your own good.

22:46.880 --> 22:48.803
MAN: How was last night, Mikey?

22:51.200 --> 22:53.248
MOLLY: And what about your own good?

22:54.960 --> 22:57.300
Janet Marie Jones.

22:57.400 --> 23:01.180
(VOICES, INDISTINCT)

23:01.280 --> 23:03.521
(GUTTURAL VOICE) Janet Marie Jones.

23:09.600 --> 23:11.762
(VOICES CONTINUE)

23:16.360 --> 23:18.089
MAN: Everything okay?

23:19.840 --> 23:23.180
- (VOICES CONTINUE)
- Janet, is everything okay?

23:23.280 --> 23:25.851
Do you want us to call someone?

23:27.920 --> 23:29.780
No. No. No.

23:29.880 --> 23:31.530
I'm, um... I'm fine.

23:32.240 --> 23:34.049
(GASPING)

23:34.160 --> 23:36.481
- Are you all right?
- Yes!

23:36.600 --> 23:38.409
I said yes.

23:38.520 --> 23:40.329
Get her processed, please. Now.

23:45.920 --> 23:47.684
WOMAN: Janet, what happened?

23:55.560 --> 23:57.847
(WHIMPERING)

24:02.080 --> 24:04.401
- (PA: FEEDBACK)
- WOMAN: Lights out.

24:06.440 --> 24:10.445
(PATIENTS MOANING, BABBLING)

24:23.720 --> 24:25.688
- (BANGS ON DOOR)
- Keep it down in there!

24:44.240 --> 24:47.369
(MOANING, BABBLING CONTINUE)

24:55.440 --> 24:56.965
(LOCK CLICKS)

24:59.240 --> 25:00.969
- MAN: Shut up!
- (BANGING)

25:03.920 --> 25:06.571
- (BANGING CONTINUES)
- Be quiet!

25:08.960 --> 25:11.930
(MOANING, BABBLING CONTINUE)

25:20.960 --> 25:24.043
(SCRATCHING)

25:35.800 --> 25:38.167
- (SCRATCHING CONTINUES)
- (GRUNTING)

25:39.960 --> 25:42.327
(DISTORTED VOICE) Molly. Molly.

25:44.520 --> 25:46.204
Molly.

25:47.760 --> 25:50.286
Molly.

25:51.120 --> 25:52.645
Molly! (ECHOING)

25:54.560 --> 25:58.201
(VOICE CONTINUES)

26:03.680 --> 26:06.650
(THUMPING)

26:08.680 --> 26:12.002
Molly. Molly.

26:12.960 --> 26:17.900
(CHANTING) Molly. Molly. Molly.

26:18.000 --> 26:21.243
(VOICE CONTINUES)

26:28.000 --> 26:29.525
We're getting stronger.

27:04.080 --> 27:05.844
(SCREAMS, GASPS)

27:07.760 --> 27:09.220
(WHIMPERS)

27:09.320 --> 27:10.845
No! (GASPING)

27:13.360 --> 27:16.300
- (PATIENTS SCREAMING)
- (THUMPING)

27:16.400 --> 27:18.980
Oh, my God! Oh, my God!

27:19.080 --> 27:22.402
Oh, God. Excuse... Excuse me! Excuse me!

27:23.840 --> 27:25.740
Someone help me!

27:25.840 --> 27:27.649
Someone help me, please!

27:27.760 --> 27:30.260
- Oh, my God! Oh, my God.
- (SCREAMING GROWS LOUDER)

27:30.360 --> 27:32.283
Somebody help me! Get out!

27:33.440 --> 27:35.966
Get out! (SCREAMING, INDISTINCT)

27:39.320 --> 27:43.530
- (KEYS JINGLE)
- (DOOR UNLOCKS)

27:55.960 --> 27:58.486
Hello, Molly. I'm Dr. Laurie Hawthorne.

27:59.600 --> 28:01.420
I know who you are.

28:01.520 --> 28:04.340
I'll be meeting with you several times
a week while you're here...

28:04.440 --> 28:07.569
for evaluation as we prep you
for your future beyond these walls.

28:09.120 --> 28:11.122
You aren't scared to be in here with me?

28:12.560 --> 28:14.020
Should I be?

28:14.120 --> 28:16.180
You read the file?

28:16.280 --> 28:17.520
I have.

28:19.800 --> 28:22.900
Says here you had a complete
and total mental breakdown...

28:23.000 --> 28:25.526
A breakdown that started
on your 24th birthday.

28:25.640 --> 28:27.130
Is that right?

28:29.160 --> 28:31.780
We'll be evaluating you here with us
for the next 30 days.

28:31.880 --> 28:34.247
I'm... I won't be here that long.

28:35.440 --> 28:36.930
What is it, Molly?

28:38.120 --> 28:40.100
Whatever it is, we're here
to help you through it,

28:40.200 --> 28:42.043
to help you to the next stage.

28:43.000 --> 28:45.420
What do you mean, the next stage?

28:45.520 --> 28:47.010
Of your life.

28:49.800 --> 28:52.460
Molly, your father committed suicide
in a mental institution...

28:52.560 --> 28:55.086
after he was found guilty
of murdering your mother.

28:56.600 --> 28:58.660
How much do you remember of that?

28:58.760 --> 29:00.220
Does my file tell you...

29:00.320 --> 29:02.540
that my parents
were also into the occult?

29:02.640 --> 29:04.324
Of course.

29:05.240 --> 29:07.420
I'm not insane, Dr. Hawthorne.

29:07.520 --> 29:09.020
I don't think that you are.

29:09.120 --> 29:10.645
I'm possessed.

29:12.200 --> 29:13.700
Molly, multiple personalities are...

29:13.800 --> 29:16.201
(SCOFFS) You think you can help me?

29:17.720 --> 29:21.500
You have no idea
what you're dealing with.

29:21.600 --> 29:24.968
(SIGHS)
Molly, I can only help you if you're...

29:38.920 --> 29:41.207
I had a counselor like you once.

29:42.400 --> 29:43.925
In high school.

29:46.320 --> 29:48.687
She thought she knew
what was best for me too.

29:57.040 --> 29:59.042
She's dead now.

30:08.200 --> 30:10.660
WOMAN: Doctor! Doctor!

30:10.760 --> 30:12.780
Doctor. Doctor. Doctor!

30:12.880 --> 30:15.406
(BABBLING, GASPING)

30:17.800 --> 30:19.450
Doctor! (GRUNTS)

30:28.360 --> 30:31.820
Hartley's counselor, Dr. Emerson,
boyfriend, Joseph Young,

30:31.920 --> 30:35.100
were eventually found
to have ties to the occult.

30:35.200 --> 30:37.362
Both were found dead
in a bizarre double suicide...

30:37.480 --> 30:40.660
shortly after Hartley
escaped from their cult...

30:40.760 --> 30:43.809
and moved to Michigan
to start a new life.

30:46.600 --> 30:48.045
(GROANS)

30:55.040 --> 30:57.520
(THUNDERCLAP)

31:04.040 --> 31:07.020
(WHISPERING PRAYER)

31:07.120 --> 31:09.327
(CONTINUES)

31:43.760 --> 31:45.762
(SCREAMS)

31:47.480 --> 31:49.005
She did this.

31:51.120 --> 31:53.043
She brought him here.

31:54.600 --> 31:56.682
We need to do something.

32:08.560 --> 32:10.449
(RAGGED BREATHING)

32:37.800 --> 32:40.565
HAWTHORNE: Molly, today I would like
to talk about your past.

32:41.680 --> 32:43.887
I'd like to talk about the occult.

32:45.240 --> 32:47.447
I want you to know
that I am not like them.

32:48.760 --> 32:50.330
You can trust me.

32:51.600 --> 32:53.090
I want what's best for you.

32:55.240 --> 32:57.460
Do you know that, Molly?

32:57.560 --> 33:00.291
I'm here to help you through this.

33:01.880 --> 33:05.202
(SCRATCHING, GURGLING)

33:07.280 --> 33:08.327
Molly?

33:09.480 --> 33:12.324
- (EXHALES)
- Molly?

33:13.440 --> 33:17.081
- (GURGLING CONTINUES)
- Molly, are you okay?

33:20.600 --> 33:21.931
What's happening?

33:25.920 --> 33:29.891
(ROARS)

33:38.120 --> 33:39.770
Oh!

33:47.080 --> 33:49.082
(DISTORTED) My master says hello.

33:50.040 --> 33:53.601
(SCREAMS)

34:00.720 --> 34:03.291
Our Father, which art in heaven,

34:03.960 --> 34:05.500
hallowed be thy name.

34:05.600 --> 34:10.179
Thy kingdom come, thy will be done
in earth as it is in heaven.

34:10.280 --> 34:11.860
Give us this day our daily bread...

34:11.960 --> 34:16.940
and forgive us our trespasses as we
forgive them who trespass against us.

34:17.040 --> 34:21.260
And lead us not into temptation,
but deliver us from evil.

34:21.360 --> 34:23.500
For thine is the kingdom
and the power and the glory,

34:23.600 --> 34:25.340
forever and ever.

34:25.440 --> 34:26.659
Amen.

34:26.760 --> 34:29.411
(GROWLING, SNARLING, FAINT)

34:38.360 --> 34:39.690
Stop it.

34:41.960 --> 34:43.324
Stop it.

34:44.760 --> 34:46.739
(GROWLING, SNARLING CONTINUE)

34:46.840 --> 34:48.330
Stop it.

34:49.840 --> 34:51.001
Stop it.

34:52.239 --> 34:53.580
Stop!

34:53.679 --> 34:55.364
Stop it!

35:04.720 --> 35:09.300
(THUMPING, FAINT)

35:09.400 --> 35:10.900
(INTERCOM BEEPS)

35:11.000 --> 35:13.685
MAN: Dr. Hawthorne,
you've got to come see this.

35:15.400 --> 35:17.209
On my way.

35:20.240 --> 35:22.971
(THUMPING CONTINUES)

35:32.280 --> 35:33.691
Oh, my God.

35:53.600 --> 35:54.601
Molly?

35:56.680 --> 35:57.681
Molly.

36:00.880 --> 36:01.881
Molly!

36:04.440 --> 36:05.726
Molly.

36:07.080 --> 36:08.605
- Stop!
- (ROARING)

36:14.080 --> 36:16.287
(CAWING)

36:18.320 --> 36:22.500
(MOLLY GROANING, SCREAMING)

36:22.600 --> 36:24.380
WOMAN: Molly, settle down.

36:24.480 --> 36:25.686
(SCREAMS)

36:33.840 --> 36:35.524
(SCREAMING CONTINUES)

36:49.120 --> 36:51.646
(GROWLS)

37:03.000 --> 37:05.321
(SCREECHES)

37:18.440 --> 37:20.681
Hello, Molly. How are you feeling?

37:20.800 --> 37:22.165
(LOCK CLICKS)

37:26.800 --> 37:30.140
I'm sorry I had to do this,
but it's for your own protection.

37:30.240 --> 37:33.220
You hurt yourself badly.

37:33.320 --> 37:37.420
In rereading the transcripts of your case,
I was struck by something.

37:37.520 --> 37:39.420
You claimed that on your 18th birthday,

37:39.520 --> 37:42.660
you were essentially
possessed by the devil.

37:42.760 --> 37:44.000
Correct?

37:48.800 --> 37:52.361
But you testified you believed
that this was only the first phase.

37:53.520 --> 37:56.300
You quoted your school counselor,
Dr. Emerson,

37:56.400 --> 37:58.100
the woman who betrayed you,

37:58.200 --> 38:01.380
as saying, "We have watched you grow.

38:01.480 --> 38:04.300
There are great things ahead.

38:04.400 --> 38:06.402
You are the one."

38:08.120 --> 38:10.940
You said in court that you've come
to believe that what she meant by that...

38:11.040 --> 38:15.523
was that you will be the one who will
return Satan to this mortal coil.

38:17.760 --> 38:19.250
Is that correct?

38:20.920 --> 38:24.811
You believe your possession on your
18th birthday is like a pregnancy...

38:26.680 --> 38:29.684
A pregnancy you thought would come
to term in your 24th year.

38:32.560 --> 38:34.460
Don't you see, Molly?

38:34.560 --> 38:39.009
Maybe this is some sort of psychosomatic
self-fulfilling prophecy.

38:40.240 --> 38:43.980
You believed this would happen
on your 24th birthday,

38:44.080 --> 38:46.340
so now your mind is willing it to be.

38:46.440 --> 38:49.728
And it's manifesting physically
with the vomiting and the noises.

38:51.720 --> 38:57.568
Why else would this... this possession
need to incubate from 18 to 24?

38:59.840 --> 39:01.410
Can you tell me why, Molly?

39:04.520 --> 39:05.567
Molly?

39:06.800 --> 39:09.804
I have been thinking about it.

39:12.360 --> 39:13.964
And?

39:15.440 --> 39:17.700
It's because it's six years later.

39:17.800 --> 39:23.340
Six years, six months,
six days, to be exact.

39:23.440 --> 39:25.442
666.

39:29.960 --> 39:33.442
But six months and six days
after your 24th birthday...

39:34.440 --> 39:36.340
That's only a few days away.

39:36.440 --> 39:39.125
(GASPS, GROANS)

39:39.240 --> 39:40.810
- (GROWLING)
- Stop.

39:43.280 --> 39:45.248
Molly, I can't understand
what you're saying.

39:45.360 --> 39:48.170
(GRUNTING)

39:48.280 --> 39:50.660
I can't understand
what you're saying, Molly.

39:50.760 --> 39:56.300
(GROANING) Stop it! Stop it!

39:56.400 --> 39:57.640
Molly?

40:01.160 --> 40:03.322
- Molly.
- (GASPS)

40:05.320 --> 40:08.847
(GRUNTS, GROWLS)

40:10.440 --> 40:12.681
He's coming!

40:15.720 --> 40:17.484
- (GLASS SHATTERS)
- (YELPS)

40:25.880 --> 40:30.363
(GROANING)

40:38.680 --> 40:42.162
(SOFTLY) "He's coming." 7:06.

40:42.760 --> 40:44.660
7:06.

40:44.760 --> 40:46.888
Sixth hour and 66 minutes.

40:48.400 --> 40:49.401
- (THUMP)
- (GASPS)

41:03.160 --> 41:05.208
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

41:09.640 --> 41:11.130
WOMAN'S VOICE: Father.

41:18.680 --> 41:20.100
Father.

41:20.200 --> 41:22.168
(VOICE, INDISTINCT)

41:34.840 --> 41:38.049
(GROWLING)

41:40.920 --> 41:42.410
(DISTORTED) Please, Father.

41:48.640 --> 41:50.700
(NORMAL) Please, Father.

41:50.800 --> 41:52.740
Help me.

41:52.840 --> 41:54.660
What'd you say?

41:54.760 --> 41:58.242
(SOFT GROWLING)

42:01.720 --> 42:04.300
Please. Please.

42:04.400 --> 42:06.448
Do what's right.

42:08.400 --> 42:11.165
MAN: Hey, Barrow. Bedtime.

42:27.480 --> 42:30.529
(GROWLING, SNARLING)

42:32.320 --> 42:34.561
(GUTTURAL LAUGHING)

42:53.360 --> 42:55.283
(GASPS) Orderly!

43:04.200 --> 43:05.326
Molly?

43:19.520 --> 43:21.045
Molly.

43:21.800 --> 43:23.245
(SCREAMS)

43:26.840 --> 43:28.683
Code gray! (SCREAMS)

43:34.880 --> 43:38.362
Help! Help!
We need restraints in here now!

43:39.720 --> 43:41.085
(SCREAMS)

43:43.080 --> 43:44.844
Help! Now!

43:45.800 --> 43:47.609
(ROARS)

43:49.520 --> 43:53.002
(GROWLING, SNARLING)

43:54.040 --> 43:57.820
(DISTORTED ROAR) I'm coming!

43:57.920 --> 44:00.730
(PANTING)

44:12.920 --> 44:15.321
(PRAYING, INDISTINCT)

44:22.680 --> 44:24.170
Excuse us, please.

44:29.240 --> 44:30.480
Father Barrow.

44:35.360 --> 44:37.980
I haven't been called that in a while.

44:38.080 --> 44:39.650
I need to talk to you right away.

44:43.880 --> 44:45.620
Of course.

44:45.720 --> 44:47.740
It's one of our other patients.

44:47.840 --> 44:49.922
Molly Hartley?

44:55.440 --> 44:58.460
Yes. I think she's possessed.

44:58.560 --> 45:00.980
Then what you need is a priest.

45:01.080 --> 45:03.500
I read that once a man is ordained
as a priest, he's always a priest.

45:03.600 --> 45:06.260
What you need is a priest
that's still ordained by the church.

45:06.360 --> 45:08.283
Things are happening.

45:10.360 --> 45:12.283
(WHISPERS) Unexplainable things.

45:17.040 --> 45:18.644
Can we talk somewhere else?

45:20.160 --> 45:22.380
I read that there are
two types of exorcisms...

45:22.480 --> 45:24.380
Solemn and unofficial.

45:24.480 --> 45:27.700
A solemn exorcism has to be
approved by the church.

45:27.800 --> 45:30.690
An unofficial exorcism
can be performed by a layperson.

45:31.680 --> 45:33.660
Someone's been doing their homework.

45:33.760 --> 45:36.700
After all the lawsuits
and bad media attention,

45:36.800 --> 45:40.980
the Roman Catholic church no longer even
teaches priests how to perform exorcisms.

45:41.080 --> 45:44.880
As of last year, there's only 17
trained exorcists in all of America.

45:45.000 --> 45:47.082
- Including me.
- Including you.

45:47.200 --> 45:48.740
- Yeah.
- And of those 17,

45:48.840 --> 45:51.180
only one has been involved
in an actual exorcism.

45:51.280 --> 45:53.408
- Me.
- You.

45:53.520 --> 45:56.580
You know the ritual of exorcism, Barrow.

45:56.680 --> 45:58.580
You no longer need approval.

45:58.680 --> 46:00.603
Think of this as your redemption.

46:02.360 --> 46:04.660
- There's no such thing.
- Please.

46:04.760 --> 46:07.047
I can't go to the cops.
They won't believe me.

46:07.160 --> 46:10.721
Just take a look at her.
This young woman, she needs you.

46:10.840 --> 46:13.100
- She's in pain.
- (SIGHS)

46:13.200 --> 46:14.690
We have no time.

46:16.000 --> 46:18.100
What about your freedom?

46:18.200 --> 46:21.204
You do this for me, I sign
your release papers. Simple as that.

46:22.400 --> 46:23.925
It's not that simple.

46:33.240 --> 46:34.969
When did this happen?

46:35.680 --> 46:37.580
Last night at 7:06.

46:37.680 --> 46:39.700
BARROW: How do you know that?

46:39.800 --> 46:41.580
HAWTHORNE:
Because all of the watches and clocks...

46:41.680 --> 46:44.100
stopped at that
exact same time last night.

46:44.200 --> 46:47.044
Sixty-six minutes after the sixth hour.

46:48.040 --> 46:50.580
JONES: He's here!

46:50.680 --> 46:53.460
His time is near!

46:53.560 --> 46:56.404
(CRYING) His time is near!

47:00.441 --> 47:03.441
Save us! (SCREAMS)

47:05.200 --> 47:08.522
(PEOPLE CLAMORING)

47:27.440 --> 47:30.820
WOMAN ON PA: Everyone to their rooms.
Lockdown in effect.

47:30.920 --> 47:33.446
(SIRENS, DISTANT)

47:37.240 --> 47:39.607
Mind if I have a moment
to talk to the patient alone?

47:41.000 --> 47:42.490
Of course.

48:26.640 --> 48:29.291
(GROWLING)

48:36.600 --> 48:40.286
(GROWLING CONTINUES)

48:42.560 --> 48:44.050
Hello, Molly.

48:45.680 --> 48:47.140
My name is John Barrow.

48:47.240 --> 48:51.848
(DISTORTED)
I know who you are, Father Barrow.

48:52.800 --> 48:54.300
I'm not an actual priest anymore.

48:54.400 --> 48:56.801
(CACKLING)

48:57.480 --> 48:59.403
So stupid.

49:00.360 --> 49:01.540
Pardon me?

49:01.640 --> 49:04.564
Like bringing a knife to a gunfight.

49:07.640 --> 49:09.900
I'm not talking to Molly, am I?

49:10.000 --> 49:11.889
No.

49:14.920 --> 49:16.620
I'd like to talk to Molly.

49:16.720 --> 49:20.566
No Molly. Only us.

49:21.520 --> 49:23.260
- (GROWLING)
- Us who?

49:23.360 --> 49:24.725
(CACKLES)

49:25.960 --> 49:28.770
"And he asked him, 'What is thy name?'

49:30.040 --> 49:34.204
And he answered, 'My name is Legion.'"
(ECHOES)

49:35.640 --> 49:40.220
- You know the Bible, I see.
- The opiate of the masses?

49:40.320 --> 49:43.700
You know what happens next
after that verse you cited?

49:43.800 --> 49:46.724
"There was nigh unto the mountain
a great herd of swine.

49:48.200 --> 49:51.807
And forthwith, Jesus sent the demons
into the swine.

49:53.520 --> 49:56.603
And the herd ran violently into the sea,
and they drowned in the waters."

49:56.720 --> 50:00.770
(CACKLES) Yeah. Poor little piggies.

50:02.520 --> 50:05.410
But I like that very much.

50:05.560 --> 50:07.801
- You do?
- Yeah.

50:09.800 --> 50:12.610
And now they sent a pauper
for the prince!

50:14.840 --> 50:17.300
(GROWLS)

50:17.400 --> 50:20.460
You're referring to the fact
I'm no longer a priest.

50:20.560 --> 50:22.403
(SIGHS)

50:23.280 --> 50:24.700
Dr. Hawthorne told you that.

50:24.800 --> 50:26.300
(CACKLES)

50:26.400 --> 50:31.620
The things they tell
in the bowels of hell, Barrow.

50:31.720 --> 50:35.805
Call Johnny Milton. I just wrote
another verse for his doggerel about me.

50:36.800 --> 50:39.963
- Paradise Lost.
- Paradise now.

50:41.440 --> 50:44.780
Paradise right here and now.

50:44.880 --> 50:46.540
(SIGHS)

50:46.640 --> 50:50.326
Paradise, right here, right now.
Come here.

50:50.440 --> 50:53.460
(GRUNTING) Come here.
I'll show you what I mean.

50:53.560 --> 50:55.460
(LAUGHS)

50:55.560 --> 50:57.020
You cannot seduce me, demon.

50:57.120 --> 51:00.820
(LAUGHING) Oh, yeah.

51:00.920 --> 51:03.540
Is Molly in there with you?

51:03.640 --> 51:06.700
- I'd like to talk to Molly.
- Why, so you can help her?

51:06.800 --> 51:08.660
I would like to talk to Molly.

51:08.760 --> 51:12.580
So you can help her like you tried
to help the others? (GASPS)

51:12.680 --> 51:14.380
(MAN'S VOICE) What have you done?

51:14.480 --> 51:16.323
My wife! My baby!

51:19.240 --> 51:21.811
(DISTORTED VOICE)
You're nothing but a failure, priest!

51:23.960 --> 51:25.962
I wanna see Molly Hartley.

51:26.520 --> 51:29.808
(SCREAMS)

51:31.840 --> 51:34.241
(PANTING) Please help me.

51:34.360 --> 51:36.940
(GROWLING)

51:37.040 --> 51:39.740
(LAUGHING)

51:39.840 --> 51:43.900
Did you enjoy that, Barrow?
Was it everything you hoped for?

51:44.000 --> 51:46.020
She's stronger than you think.

51:46.120 --> 51:48.540
She's in there,
and I'm gonna help her out.

51:48.640 --> 51:50.802
(SCREAMING, ROARING)

51:50.920 --> 51:53.207
Ah!

51:55.800 --> 51:58.963
(SCREAMING, ROARING CONTINUE)

52:04.920 --> 52:06.888
Was Molly an exceptional student?

52:07.760 --> 52:09.740
HAWTHORNE: That's the thing.

52:09.840 --> 52:13.322
In high school, she was
an average student. Nothing special.

52:13.440 --> 52:16.250
Then on her 18th birthday,
everything changed.

52:16.360 --> 52:18.580
Wharton School of Business,
straight A's.

52:18.680 --> 52:21.923
Graduated a semester early,
magna cum laude.

52:23.320 --> 52:25.740
Hired on at a top financial firm
shortly afterward...

52:25.840 --> 52:28.540
and made partner at 24.

52:28.640 --> 52:33.089
It's almost like she had some sort
of helping hand along the way.

52:33.760 --> 52:35.285
What about in literature?

52:36.920 --> 52:39.420
John Milton, Paradise Lost?

52:39.520 --> 52:41.940
It's doubtful she'd have
any of that knowledge.

52:42.040 --> 52:44.020
Not from business school, anyway.

52:44.120 --> 52:46.885
I have to review her high school
academic file further.

52:50.360 --> 52:52.249
So what do you think?

52:53.320 --> 52:55.561
If you don't mind,
I'd like to see somebody.

52:56.960 --> 52:59.691
Consult with. Confidentially, of course.

53:00.840 --> 53:04.447
(BELL CHIMING)

53:21.600 --> 53:23.125
BARROW: Chaplain Davies.

53:24.440 --> 53:25.965
(SIGHS)

53:27.440 --> 53:30.444
- They let you out?
- Not exactly.

53:32.520 --> 53:34.940
What brings the prodigal son here to me?

53:35.040 --> 53:38.940
I think there's a patient at Clovesdale
that needs an exorcism.

53:39.040 --> 53:44.126
I don't care if she spoke the entire Bible
backwards in Aramaic.

53:44.240 --> 53:48.500
There's no way the church is going
to approve an exorcism in this day and age.

53:48.600 --> 53:51.860
- I know.
- Then what are you doing here?

53:51.960 --> 53:54.560
Because in my experience,
the girl is possessed.

53:54.660 --> 53:56.540
So help her.

53:56.640 --> 53:58.980
But know what you're doing
might have serious consequences.

53:59.080 --> 54:00.900
I know, but I'm not a priest anymore.

54:01.000 --> 54:04.368
Don't have to be in the NBA
to play basketball, right?

54:06.240 --> 54:09.980
Is your reluctance really
to do with what happened last time?

54:10.080 --> 54:11.780
Yeah.

54:11.880 --> 54:13.166
It is.

54:18.560 --> 54:19.561
Wait here.

54:20.840 --> 54:22.842
I have something for you.

54:56.320 --> 54:59.722
I kept these for you,
locked up down there.

55:07.160 --> 55:12.820
God, wash away the iniquities of this
building and cleanse it from its sins,

55:12.920 --> 55:15.500
taking away all place
of refuge for the dark one...

55:15.600 --> 55:19.127
as he's vanquished from your
humble servant, Molly Hartley.

55:20.520 --> 55:22.940
(PANTING) Please,

55:23.040 --> 55:25.860
come to my assistance
who you've created in your likeness...

55:25.960 --> 55:28.300
and who you've redeemed
at a great price...

55:28.400 --> 55:31.085
from the tyranny of the devil.

55:47.920 --> 55:51.288
(LOCK CLICKS)

56:01.480 --> 56:02.925
(GROWLING)

56:06.840 --> 56:08.808
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

56:11.280 --> 56:13.931
(GRUNTING)

56:16.440 --> 56:19.284
(GROWLING, ROARING)

56:28.680 --> 56:30.780
Why don't you untie me now?

56:30.880 --> 56:34.820
Are you gonna wait for the cock
to crow three times,

56:34.920 --> 56:37.491
like that fool who founded your church?

56:38.520 --> 56:40.420
I'm with no church.

56:40.520 --> 56:46.140
I come armed only with the faith in the Lord
that banished you to the bowels of hell.

56:46.240 --> 56:48.607
(ROARS)

56:54.720 --> 56:56.688
(EXHALES)

57:12.160 --> 57:14.540
Most glorious prince
of the heavenly armies,

57:14.640 --> 57:17.420
defend me in my battle
against principalities and powers,

57:17.520 --> 57:20.420
against the rulers of this dark world,

57:20.520 --> 57:23.940
against the spirit of wickedness
in the high places.

57:24.040 --> 57:26.691
(ROOSTER CROWS)

57:27.560 --> 57:29.927
(LAUGHS)

57:32.760 --> 57:34.820
The supplicant's position.

57:34.920 --> 57:37.940
The perfect place for a meager servant.

57:38.040 --> 57:42.011
Do you want to kiss my ring? Or my lips?

57:43.200 --> 57:45.851
- You can have any of this!
- Silence, demon.

57:47.920 --> 57:51.100
In the name of the Father,
the Son and the Holy Spirit,

57:51.200 --> 57:52.740
as it was in the beginning,

57:52.840 --> 57:55.740
as it is now and ever shall be,
world with no end.

57:55.840 --> 57:59.220
- Amen.
- (ROARING)

57:59.320 --> 58:02.260
Why did you fail me, Barrow?

58:02.360 --> 58:05.620
Please, Barrow, stop this.
This is no way to help your flock.

58:05.720 --> 58:09.340
- You know how this will end.
- You can't fool me again, demon.

