01:15:38.200 --> 01:15:39.964
Leviathan?

01:15:40.800 --> 01:15:44.100
L-V-T-Y-N. Leviathan.

01:15:44.200 --> 01:15:46.123
(GROWLING)

01:15:48.960 --> 01:15:51.860
Members of the Church of Satan
adorn themselves with the symbol.

01:15:51.960 --> 01:15:53.460
What is Leviathan?

