with her slain blood...

01:26:34.520 --> 01:26:37.180
- No, hey.
- The Leviathan shall arise!

01:26:37.280 --> 01:26:38.620
Let her go!

01:26:38.720 --> 01:26:41.405
- (BLADE STABBING FLESH)
- (GRUNTS)

